# Git commits

Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` or any co-author trailer to commits. Netlify blocks builds from commits with unrecognized contributors on private repos.

All commits must be authored and committed solely as:
- Name: Xmichael23
- Email: michaelangelos@gmail.com

If using git from the agent, use `git commit-tree` (not `git commit`) to avoid tooling that injects co-author trailers.
